# promote init demo
Output demo/init.gif
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 900
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 40ms
Set Shell zsh

Type "npx tsx src/index.ts init"
Enter
Sleep 4s

# Select Anthropic (Claude)
Down 2
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 1s

# Select Korean
Down 2
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 1s

# Balanced threshold
Down 1
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 1s

# Claude Code
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 1s

# Path scoped dir — accept default
Enter
Sleep 1s

# ADR dir — accept default
Enter
Sleep 1s

# Create CLAUDE.md? Yes
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 2s

# Done
Sleep 3s
